    <note type="biography">
        <p>Naval officer. Born in Cape Colony. Acting mate on HMS <hi rend="italic">Beagle</hi>, 1836. Lieutenant on HMS <hi rend="italic">Princess Charlotte</hi> in the Mediterranean, 1840–1. Served off the coast of England, 1842–7. Commander on HMS <hi rend="italic">Driver</hi> in the Pacific, 1848–52. Captain, 1856; rear-admiral, 1875; vice-admiral, 1879. Retired in 1864.</p></note>
